          Update Scout agent documentation to include E11 conflict prevention guidance.

          ### 1. Add E11 Prevention Section

          In `implementations/claude-code/prompts/agents/scout.md`, find the section
          "7. Assign file ownership and agent IDs" (around line 230) and add a new
